---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Closed-List App">
  <main class="container mx-auto p-4 max-w-2xl mt-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-blue-600 mb-6">
      歡迎來到 Closed-List App
    </h1>
    <p class="text-center text-lg text-gray-600">
      這是您的個人化封閉式清單應用程式。
    </p>
    <div class="mt-10 p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">今日清單</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500">此處將顯示今日的封閉式任務。</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>